  "instructions": [
    "Heat a tava-griddle over medium heat. ",
    "Add 1 tablespoon of ghee and swirl it around to coat the pan.",
    "Add the chopped onions and cook until caramelized, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the berbere spice mix and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the collard greens, smoked salt, and a pinch of black pepper. ",
    "Cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally, until the greens are tender.",
    "Stir in the niter kibbeh, pumpkin seeds, grated coconut, and crispy onions.",
    "Season with kosher salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the gomen to a serving platter and garnish with chopped cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately, with a side of injera bread if desired."
  ],
